These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, techno, electronic, salsa
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, august, september, july
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, turkish, british, canadian
1. the pakistani is the fan of salsa##1
2. the british is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
6. the canadian is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
7. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in july and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | salsa      | jazz | techno | electronic |
| Birthday   | september | april  | august   | july    |
| Nationality     | pakistani     | british    | canadian    | turkish      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, dubstep, rock
4 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, domino, backgammon
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, snowboarding, parkour
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
2. the fan of rock is the person playing domino##1
3. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
6. the fan of house is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
7. the person playing monopoly is between the fan of rock and the fan of house##2
8. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing bridge and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | rock | dubstep   | house | r&b  |
| Game   | domino     | monopoly | backgammon  | bridge |
| Sport     | parkour        | snowboarding  | lacrosse    | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, almond-milk, mirinda
House: modern, victorian, art-deco, cottage
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, lily, iris
1. the cottage house is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the victorian house is the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
6. the art-deco house is between the person drinking juice and the modern house##2
7. the cottage house is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | 7up | juice   | mirinda     | almond-milk     |
| House   | victorian  | cottage | art-deco   | modern  |
| Flower     | iris      | aconite | lily | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, video-games, collecting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, rose, azalea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, game, davidoff, aristoff
1. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the game-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
5. the person who growsazalea is the cain-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | camping  | collecting   | video-games     | skydiving |
| Flower   | rose  | azalea      | daisy        | iris     |
| Cigar         | davidoff | cain | aristoff | game   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, november, may
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, artichoke, grapes, cabbage
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, lily, orchid
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsazalea is the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
6. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
9. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Birthday   | june   | may   | november | october |
| Food         | artichoke      | cabbage | blueberry      | grapes |
| Flower     | daffodil | azalea        | orchid       | lily  |

