.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, architect, journalist, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cycling, volleyball, badminton
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, daisy, rose
1. the architect is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the architect##1
4. the journalist is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
6. the musician is on the left of the architect##1
7. the musician is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job    | journalist   | musician      | architect       | photographer |
| Sport   | parkour | badminton | volleyball     | cycling |
| Flower     | rose     | tulip  | daffodil | daisy |

