.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, videographer, social-worker, analyst
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, august, may
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, dutch, chinese, italian
1. the chinese is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the dutch is between the person who's birthday is in may and the spanish##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the videographer##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the videographer##3
5. the journalist is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the analyst##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is the journalist##1
8. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Job      | social-worker   | analyst          | videographer | journalist        |
| Birthday   | august     | september | may   | april     |
| Nationality           | spanish | dutch         | italian         | chinese |

