.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, indian, australian
4 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, hedgehog, cat
4 different games are played: domino, scrabble, billiard, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the american##1
3. the owner of the cat is the indian##1
4. the indian is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the owner of the snake and the american##2
6. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
7. the american is in an even position##4
8. the american is between the british and the indian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality         | british | american      | indian       | australian    |
| Pet           | goldfish  | hedgehog  | cat | snake |
| Game   | poker      | billiard | scrabble         | domino    |

