.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
House: gothic-revival, victorian, ranch-style, tower
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, brazilian, japanese
City: liverpool, paris, venice, hannover
1. the american is in an odd position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the american##3
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the american##1
7. the american is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the canadian is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
9. the japanese is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| House   | victorian         | gothic-revival  | ranch-style     | tower         |
| Nationality        | japanese | canadian | american | brazilian         |
| City      | paris         | venice  | liverpool   | hannover |

