.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
City: new-york, rome, liverpool, marseilles
There 4 different types of food: pepper, eggplant, cherry, lime
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, turquise, black, yellow
 1. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
 2. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the person eating cherry is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to new-york##2
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 6. the person who likes yellow is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating eggplant is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to liverpool##2
10. the person who likes black is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| City   | new-york  | liverpool    | rome | marseilles    |
| Food   | pepper | cherry | eggplant  | lime |
| Color           | black   | yellow    | light-blue        | turquise   |

