.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana, old-henry, cain
There 4 different types of food: corn, onion, lime, tomato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy, spy, action
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating corn##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
4. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person eating corn##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating onion##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person eating onion##1
8. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
9. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar      | baccarat                | cain  | havana | old-henry   |
| Food           | tomato | onion | corn   | lime |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy         | horror     | action     | spy |

