.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, parkour, cricket, swimming
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, argentine, australian, pakistani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea, coffee
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the pakistani and the person drinking coffee##2
6. the australian is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | cricket    | parkour  | swimming  | tennis |
| Nationality   | pakistani | argentine | thai | australian |
| Beverage   | tea    | hot-chocolate     | coffee    | lemonade |

