.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, jazz, ambient
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bike, trike, jet-ski
House: farmhouse, townhouse, victorian, gothic-revival
1. the townhouse house is between the fan of jazz and the person driving the ship##2
2. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
8. the person driving the trike is the fan of indie##1
9. the person driving the jet-ski is between the victorian house and the farmhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre      | indie | jazz      | blues  | ambient    |
| Transport   | trike   | bike | jet-ski | ship |
| House           | gothic-revival      | victorian       | townhouse   | farmhouse      |

