.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, fonseca, game, vegafina
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, rose, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance, thriller, epic
1. the game-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the fonseca-smoker is between the vegafina-smoker and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the person who growsaconite is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person who growsbegonia##2
7. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
9. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | alhambra    | game | fonseca  | vegafina  |
| Flower   | rose | marigold       | aconite | begonia |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller   | fantasy      | epic | romance       |

