The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, august, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, sailing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar      | davidoff      | dunhill | prince     | oliveros    |
| Birthday   | july | november      | december | august |
| Sport           | sailing   | soccer  | weightlifting     | badminton |

