.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, disco, punk, house
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, camping, woodworking, gardening
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, siglo, fonseca, montecristo
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the fan of disco is between the siglo-smoker and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
6. the prince-smoker is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
7. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre    | punk    | disco     | hip-hop    | house        |
| Hobby       | woodworking   | chess | camping | gardening |
| Cigar   | montecristo | fonseca      | siglo    | prince   |

