.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, domino, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, baking, rock-climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, bus, boat
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the subway and the person playing backgammon##2
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
4. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game          | whist | backgammon  | mah-jongg   | domino    |
| Hobby   | singing  | baking     | rock-climbing | hiking |
| Transport   | bus   | boat | helicopter | subway   |

