4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes azure##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
