4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the person eating asparagus is the analyst##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the chef##1
7. the chef is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
8. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food   | tomato | carrot | asparagus | radish   |
| Color   | lilac    | white   | apricot     | turquise    |
| Job   | nurse  | chef | analyst  | accountant |

