.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, country, rock, electronic
House: modern, futuristic, cape-cod, cottage
City: miami, edinburgh, san-francisco, liverpool
1. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
2. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the modern house##3
4. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
5. the fan of country is between the cottage house and the modern house##2
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the modern house##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the fan of pop##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre    | rock    | country    | pop  | electronic |
| House   | cottage | futuristic | modern | cape-cod      |
| City     | edinburgh   | miami        | liverpool   | san-francisco       |

 